Maintaining strategic communication, enhancing mutual trust and expanding cooperation will help promote the sustained healthy development of China-Europe relations, Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesperson Zhao Lijian said on Friday. Several Chinese companies have recently announced that they will issue Global Depository Receipts (GDRs) and plan to get listed in Switzerland and Germany. In this episode of BizBeat, CGTN's Kate Kui believes the issuance of GDRs by Chinese companies symbolizes closer ties between China and Europe, and plenty of other future cooperation areas are expected.